{"tid":1870682,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"【行動】火炭駿洋邨隔離營 居民大會","createTime":"2020-02-09T04:28:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T04:07:10.000Z","uid":133867,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"4bbf67997ae074ea3493890e57fd8ec49e0a9c1d","tid":1870682,"uid":133867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T04:28:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">火炭駿洋邨將成為隔離營</span></span><br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥<span style=\"color: red;\">出爾反爾</span>，佢喺1月28日既時候講過盡量不用未入伙既公屋邨作為檢疫中心設施，但係琴日2月8日就因為疫情發展不能預見，就想用火炭新落成公屋駿洋邨成為隔離營。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">火炭駿洋邨</span>位於火炭工業區，最近屋邨既華生工業大廈，入面有幾間大型既食品加工場同製造食品公司。琴日有報導指出<span style=\"color: purple;\">病毒有機會由空氣傳播</span>，所以<span style=\"color: red;\">唔排除</span>會污染食品，或經由車輛將病菌帶到市區。<br />\n<br />\n另外，附近亦有公共交通工具到各區，例如:<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">280x到九龍、尖沙咀<br />\n80m 到 九龍塘<br />\n798 到 將軍澳<br />\n88x 到 藍田<br />\n481 到 荃灣</span><br />\n可見，將病毒、病菌傳染途徑廣泛！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日下午四點火炭山尾街遊樂場</span></span><br />\n將會舉行居民大會，除咗火炭居民之外，希望其他區既居民可以助火炭一臂之力，大家都可以到場抗議！反抗！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OSU7XQ2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOSU7XQ2.jpg&h=5b58186a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/78MY4v6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F78MY4v6.jpg&h=cae3f3b6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bgujOXQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbgujOXQ.jpg&h=7aa85719&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be21388fd28530d60f5765bbc88e813c3c926d6a","tid":1870682,"uid":21483,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T04:31:14.000Z","msg":"［非分化］當美孚被選為隔離營既時候，火炭人去左邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c5d7e74fe259b6b4ef22a6ef3b316c7a699c11","tid":1870682,"uid":133867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote